Why OpenRIPD ?


I needed it

We want allow the users who want to use RIP, to do it in a secure way

There was no satisfying daemons for RIP
routed
lacks any kind of authetication
zebra, quagga
weak sequence number handling and generation
you still want to use them? :)
xorp
weak sequence number handling and generation	

The framework used for routing daemons in OpenBSD is proved secure, fast and reliable

